videos.description: UConn goes 90 feet in three passes without needing a dribble for the easy layup by Kia Nurse extending the Huskies' lead to 30 over SMU.
videos.headline: UConn runs fast break to perfection without needing a dribble
Defense leads to offense for UCONN

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson and Geno Auriemma react to UConn reaching a historic 91 straight wins, with Auriemma pointing towards the history of the programming setting this milestone up.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (Geno: UConn's history got them to 91 wins) 2017/1/14 SC
